    "type": "spell",
    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You afflict the target with the curse of the roiling, unforgiving sea. The target must attempt a Will save.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Critical Success</b>  The target is unaffected.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Success</b>  The target becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened} 1. Reducing its @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened} condition to 0 ends the curse.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Failure</b>  The target becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened} 1 and can't reduce its @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened} condition below 1 while the curse remains. The curse can be lifted by remove curse or similar magic. Whenever the target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened} and on the water at least a mile from shore, it is also @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed} 1.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Critical Failure</b>  As failure, but the target becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened} 2.</p>",
